casebody.data:
Larry WHITFIELD, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-9026. Supreme Court of the United States June 23, 2014. Case below, 548 Fed.Appx. 70 . Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
